One big software

Split into  
  - Watchlist
  - Portfolio Tracker
  - Comparison

Watchlist
  - Add/Remove Stocks
  - View Stocks
  - View Stock Details
  - View Stock Graph
  - Add comments to stocks

Portfolio Tracker
  - Display current portfolio
  - Automatically update stock prices
  - When position closed -> gets logged in trading log
  - View Trading Log
  - View Stock Graph

Comparison
  - Compare multiple stocks
  - Display stock comparison graphs 
      - Compare spread,ratios,Non rebalanced index, Relative perfomance index